1)Conditional statements
a)if statements
b)else statements
c)elif statements
d)nested if statements
e)Ternary Conditional Operator
ex - num = 7
result = "Even" if num % 2 == 0 else "Odd"
print(result)

2)Iterative statements
ans - 
a)for loop 
ex - for i in range(10):
       print(i)
b)while loop
ex - while(True):
       a=10
       if(a>1):
          print(a)
       else:
          break
3)Transfer statements
ans - 
i)pass,break and continue
